owntown%20Miami%2C%20Maile%20Aguila%20retreats%20to%20her%20five-acre%20farm%20about%2030%20miles%20south.%20The%20place%20is%20a%20far%20cry%20from%20the%20city's%20soaring%20high-rises%2C%20where%20uber-rich%20buyers%20enjoy%20access%20to%20perks%20like%20indoor%20lap%20pools%2C%20private%20padel%20courts%2C%20and%20spacious%20balconies%20overlooking%20the%20water.%20Tucked%20inside%20a%20barn%20on%20Aguila's%20property%2C%20though%2C%20is%20an%20amenity%20that%20would%20feel%20right%20at%20home%20in%20any%20penthouse%3A%20her%20prized%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fsauna-benefits%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einfrared%20sauna%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAguila%2C%2071%2C%20has%20lived%20on%20the%20property%20for%20decades%2C%20but%20she%20awoke%20to%20the%20wonders%20of%20the%20sauna%20a%20couple%20of%20months%20ago%20at%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsilicon-valley-biohacking-wellness-event-best-hacks-not-what-expected-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eevent%20hosted%20by%20Biohack%20Miami%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20walk%20out%20of%20there%2C%20you%20feel%20brand%20new%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Aguila.%20Several%20evenings%20a%20week%2C%20she%20cranks%20up%20Bad%20Bunny%20or%20Marc%20Anthony%20and%20sinks%20into%20the%20hot%20glow%20for%2020%20minutes.%20Then%20she%20enjoys%20the%20best%20sleep%20she's%20had%20in%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20twin%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flooksmaxxing-tiktok-trend-explained-men-trade-beauty-tips-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eobsessions%20with%20longevity%20and%20looksmaxxing%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20hacking%20our%20way%20to%20healthier%20lives%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgetting-hot-job-requirement-ozempic-botox-looksmaxxing-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elooking%20hotter%20while%20doing%20it%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20are%20reshaping%20not%20just%20bodies%20but%20homes%2C%20turning%20spare%20rooms%20and%20garages%20into%20dens%20of%20tech-enabled%20optimization%20rather%20than%20lo-fi%20leisure.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquiet-luxury-loud-tacky-wealth-america-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMcMansion%20era%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20its%20man%20caves%20and%20home%20movie%20theaters%3B%20the%20pandemic%20sent%20everyone%20scrambling%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-ultimate-home-office-guide-for-2024-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eset%20up%20a%20home%20office%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20a%20makeshift%20gym.%20The%20biggest%20flex%20these%20days%20is%20a%20cold%20plunge%2C%20red-light%20therapy%20room%2C%20or%20sauna.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20modern%20luxury%20markers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhome-saunas-new-luxury-status-symbol-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Earen't%20solely%20for%20the%20superrich%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It's%20never%20been%20cheaper%20to%20bring%20the%20spa%20home%3A%20the%20model%20Aguila%20bought%20fits%20two%20people%20and%20costs%20less%20than%20%245%2C000.%20I%20also%20spoke%20with%20a%2027-year-old%20Austin%20couple%20who%20transformed%20an%20empty%20covered%20patio%20into%20what%20they've%20playfully%20dubbed%20a%20%26quot%3Bwellness%20hut%2C%26quot%3B%20complete%20with%20sauna%20and%20cold%20plunge%2C%20for%20less%20than%20%248%2C000%20%E2%80%94%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20cost%20of%20a%20typical%20kitchen%20renovation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiohackers-build-house-to-help-them-live-longer-cost-features-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewealthy%20are%20all%20in%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20this%20stuff%2C%20too.%20During%20a%20recent%20trip%20to%20Miami%2C%20I%20watched%20health-conscious%20patrons%20curl%20up%20in%20hyperbaric%20oxygen%20chambers%20and%20chatted%20with%20condo%20developers%20at%20the%20bleeding%20edge%20of%20the%20wellness%20boom.%20I'm%20always%20a%20little%20wary%20of%20buzzword-y%20sales%20pitches%2C%20which%20can%20veer%20into%20the%20nonsensical%2C%20but%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbi-today-sunday-newsletter-bryan-johnson-longevity-celibacy-stigma-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elongevity%20craze%3C%2Fa%3E%20seems%20to%20have%20real%20legs.%20For%20health-obsessed%20homeowners%2C%20that%20means%20a%20host%20of%20new%20status%20symbols.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EAmerica's%20homebuyers%20are%20a%20fickle%20bunch.%20Marble%20countertops%20were%20all%20the%20rage%20until%20buyers%20warmed%20to%20quartz.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpopcorn-ceilings-home-outdated-diy-renovation-improvement-2019-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPopcorn%20ceilings%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20once%20en%20vogue%2C%20are%20now%20a%20liability.%20At%20least%20open%20floor%20plans%20are%20still%20hot%20%E2%80%94%20wait%2C%20nope%2C%20people%20suddenly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-break-up-open-floor-plan-interior-designers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewant%20defined%20living%20spaces%20again%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Home%20spa%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3a93f2d175c90a6a6fb085%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERoger%20and%20Haley%20Macin%20turned%20a%20former%20garage%20in%20their%20backyard%20into%20a%20%26quot%3Bwellness%20hut%26quot%3B%20with%20a%20cold%20plunge%20and%20sauna.%3Cp%3EBill%20McCullough%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20real-estate%20buzzword%20is%20%26quot%3Bwellness.%26quot%3B%20Mentions%20of%20the%20word%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnational-association-realtors-rules-commissions-zillow-home-search-pocket-listings-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ein%20Zillow%20listings%3C%2Fa%3E%20increased%2033%25%20last%20year%2C%20the%20home%20search%20platform%20said%2C%20while%20%26quot%3Bspa-inspired%26quot%3B%20bathrooms%20showed%20up%2022%25%20more%20often.%20The%20uptick%20likely%20reflects%20a%20couple%20of%20things%2C%20says%20Amanda%20Pendleton%2C%20Zillow's%20home-trends%20expert%3A%20More%20people%20are%20splurging%20on%20nice-to-haves%20like%20steam%20showers%20and%20wet%20rooms%2C%20while%20savvy%20real%20estate%20agents%20are%20recognizing%20the%20surge%20in%20interest%20and%20grasping%20for%20anything%20that%20could%20fall%20under%20a%20capacious%20definition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20sort%20of%20a%20mixed%20bag%2C%26quot%3B%20Pendleton%20tells%20me.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20marketing%2C%20but%20it's%20also%20that%20these%20features%20truly%20are%20more%20common%20in%20homes%20today%20than%20they%20were%20a%20year%20ago.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECold%20plunges%20and%20saunas%20are%20undeniably%20on%20the%20rise.%20The%20US%20sauna%20market%20is%20expected%20to%20grow%20in%20value%20by%20%24161.3%20million%20from%202025%20to%202030%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20from%20the%20market-intelligence%20firm%20Technavio.%20Grand%20View%20Research%2C%20a%20similar%20firm%2C%20projects%20an%20even%20bigger%20rise%20in%20the%20cold%20plunge%20segment%2C%20from%20roughly%20%24355%20million%20in%202025%20to%20%24660%20million%20by%202033.%20In%20addition%20to%20these%20mainstays%2C%20luxury%20homes%20have%20turned%20into%20testing%20grounds%20for%20more%20exotic%20amenities.%20Rich%20buyers%20are%20turning%20what%20might%20once%20have%20been%20a%20walk-in%20closet%20into%20a%20red-light%20therapy%20room%2C%20or%20swapping%20a%20hyperbaric%20chamber%20for%20a%20plush%20sofa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHigh-dollar%20condo%20developers%20are%20also%20allocating%20more%20square%20footage%20to%20amenities%20for%20buyers%20looking%20to%20optimize%20their%20health.%20Aguila's%20latest%20undertaking%20is%20selling%20units%20at%20HQ%20Residences%20Miami%2C%20a%20condo%20tower%20in%20the%20city's%20Edgewater%20neighborhood%20where%20the%20second-highest%20floor%20is%20devoted%20entirely%20to%20wellness%20rituals%20like%20the%20requisite%20hot-and-cold%20spa%20circuit%20as%20well%20as%20yoga%2C%20pilates%2C%20and%20robotic%20massages.%20The%20most%20expensive%20units%20will%20go%20for%20%242.2%20million.%20On%20the%20more%20affordable%20end%20is%20House%20of%20Wellness%2C%20another%20planned%20condo%20development%20in%20Miami%2C%20where%20units%20start%20at%20%24400%2C000.%20The%2035-floor%20tower%20will%20include%20a%20full-service%20spa%20and%20offer%20residents%20a%20personalized%20health%20assessment%20each%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLongevity%2C%20it's%20in%20our%20DNA%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Ricardo%20Dunin%2C%20the%20developer%20behind%20the%20project.%20%26quot%3BI%20mean%2C%20who%20doesn't%20want%20to%20live%20longer%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20rendering%20of%20steam%20rooms%20and%20a%20shower%20in%20a%20neutral-toned%20spa%20room%20at%20the%20planned%20House%20of%20Wellness%20condo%20development%20in%20downtown%20Miami.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a316270e826bfa433d6e6df%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222058%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20steam%20room%20and%20sauna%20at%20the%20planned%20House%20of%20Wellness%20condo%20development%20in%20downtown%20Miami.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20House%20of%20Wellness%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20outside%20Miami%2C%20I%20toured%20Oasis%20Hallandale%2C%20a%20development%20that%20includes%20two%20residential%20towers%2C%20restaurants%2C%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Bfitness%20and%20biohacking%20hub%26quot%3B%20called%20Oasis%20Fit%2C%20where%20residents%20of%20the%20condos%20%E2%80%94%20priced%20from%20%24750%2C000%20to%20%245.02%20million%20%E2%80%94%20will%20enjoy%20heavily%20discounted%20access%20to%20features%20like%20cryotherapy%2C%20peptide%20injections%2C%20several%20saunas%2C%20and%20a%20range%20of%20recovery%20treatments.%20The%20place%20leans%20more%20into%20the%20sterile%20feel%20of%20a%20doctor's%20office%20than%20the%20soothing%20tones%20of%20a%20new-age%20spa%2C%20but%20it's%20easy%20to%20imagine%20a%20resident%20spending%20a%20good%20chunk%20of%20their%20day%20there%2C%20hopping%20from%20a%20pilates%20class%20to%20the%20recovery%20room%20and%20maybe%20tacking%20on%20an%20hour%20of%20hyperbaric%20oxygen%20therapy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228688%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Infrared%20saunas%20and%20hyperbaric%20oxgen%20chambers%20line%20one%20side%20of%20the%20room%20opposite%20an%20array%20of%20recovery%20machines.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a315f666a1225644000d196%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225792%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EInfrared%20saunas%20and%20hyperbaric%20oxgen%20chambers%20line%20the%20walls%20of%20the%20Biocell%20Lab%20at%20Oasis%20Fit%20in%20Hallandale%20Beach%2C%20Florida.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Oasis%20Hallandale%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20multimillion-dollar%20homes%20may%20represent%20the%20most%20aspirational%20end%20of%20this%20shift%2C%20I%20found%20myself%20more%20struck%20by%20the%20regular%20people%20devoting%20slices%20of%20their%20living%20rooms%20or%20backyards%20to%20cheaper%2C%20prefab%20longevity%20tech.%20The%20more%20attainable%20versions%20of%20these%20status%20symbols%20are%20nonetheless%20still%20flexes%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20from%20my%20vantage%20point%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbidding-war-apartment-new-york-city-auction-rent-landlord-housing-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecramped%20New%20York%20City%20apartment%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoger%20and%20Haley%20Macin%2C%20both%2027%2C%20began%20their%20house%20hunt%20in%20Austin%20with%20dreams%20of%20finding%20a%20place%20that%20could%20accommodate%20their%20growing%20obsession%20with%20the%20cold%20plunge.%20Haley%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20had%20been%20following%20the%20work%20of%20functional%20medicine%20doctor%20Mark%20Hyman%20and%20seeking%20out%20any%20treatments%20that%20could%20reduce%20stress%20and%20anxiety%20%E2%80%94%20the%20cold%20plunge%20was%20the%20only%20thing%20she%20tried%20that%20delivered%20instant%20results.%20%26quot%3BThe%20first%20time%20I%20did%20it%2C%20I%20was%20like%2C%20'Oh%20my%20god%2C'%20Haley%20tells%20me.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20energy%20all%20day.%20My%20body%20felt%20better%2C%20my%20mind%20felt%20clearer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20found%20their%20match%20in%20a%20low-slung%2C%20two-bedroom%20home%20with%20a%20separate%20structure%20in%20the%20backyard%20that%20had%20once%20served%20as%20a%20single-car%20garage.%20Bug%20nets%20on%20the%20sides%20let%20in%20light%20while%20the%20roof%20offered%20protection%20from%20the%20elements%2C%20making%20it%20a%20prime%20spot%20for%20their%20cold%20plunge%2C%20which%20they%20purchased%20for%20roughly%20%246%2C000%20soon%20after%20moving%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20got%20a%20cold%20plunge%20before%20we%20even%20got%2C%20like%2C%20a%20guest%20bed%20or%20a%20lot%20of%20our%20furniture%2C%26quot%3B%20Haley%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20their%20big%20splurge%2C%20they've%20since%20added%20more%20features%20to%20round%20out%20what%20they%20affectionately%20call%20their%20%26quot%3Bwellness%20hut%2C%26quot%3B%20like%20a%20two-person%20infrared%20sauna%20they%20purchased%20for%20about%20%241%2C500%20and%20assembled%20themselves.%20Sometimes%20friends%20drop%20by%20to%20hang%20out%20and%20rotate%20between%20the%20heat%20and%20cold.%20Roger%20says%20he%20knows%20a%20few%20other%20people%20who%20have%20cold-plunge%20setups%2C%20and%20he%20comes%20across%20many%20other%20boosters%20on%20LinkedIn%2C%20where%20he%20spends%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20for%20work%3A%20%26quot%3BThey're%20like%2C%20'I%20live%20and%20die%20by%20the%20cold%20plunge.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3ECompact%20amenities%20like%20these%20are%20natural%20fits%20for%20the%20age%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-dream-shrinking-smaller-homes-fewer-kids-vacation-time-commutes-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshrinking%20American%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20the%20typical%20new%20house%20about%20300%20square%20feet%20smaller%20than%20it%20was%20a%20decade%20ago.%20Stressed%20out%20and%20stretched%20thin%2C%20today's%20professionals%20are%20searching%20for%20ways%20to%20maximize%20their%20space%20and%20reduce%20the%20amount%20of%20time%20they%20spend%20driving%20to%20and%20from%20the%20gym.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20work%20all%20day%2C%20so%20we%20don't%20really%20have%20time%20to%20go%20to%20another%20location%20for%20a%20workout%2C%20or%20then%20a%20third%20location%20for%20a%20sauna%20and%20cold%20plunge%2C%26quot%3B%20Roger%20tells%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224215%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Home%20spa%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3a9387d175c90a6a6fb06c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223161%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWellness%20tech%20and%20health-focused%20features%20can%20be%20a%20mixed%20bag%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20a%20home's%20value.%3Cp%3EBill%20McCullough%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20at%20least%2C%20wellness%20features%20may%20or%20may%20not%20juice%20your%20home's%20value.%20Zillow%20found%20that%20homes%20with%20cold%20plunges%20sell%20for%202%25%20more%20than%20comparable%20places%20without%20one%2C%20a%20sizable%20bump%20for%20some%20bone-chilling%20water.%20A%20sauna%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20was%20associated%20with%20a%200.2%25%20%3Cem%3Edecrease%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20value.%20Homebuyers%2C%20Pendleton%20says%2C%20may%20be%20willing%20to%20%26quot%3Bpay%20above%20and%20beyond%20for%20a%20home%20with%20wellness%20features%20they're%20actually%20going%20to%20use%2C%20but%20they're%20not%20going%20to%20pay%20for%20a%20sauna%20if%20that's%20not%20their%20vibe%2C%20right%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOK%2C%20so%20clearly%20some%20can't%20handle%20the%20heat%20(or%20simply%20don't%20want%20an%20entire%20room%20devoted%20to%20it).%20My%20time%20in%20Miami%20made%20clear%20that%20homeowners%20these%20days%20have%20a%20broad%20range%20of%20options%20at%20their%20fingertips.%20Aguila%2C%20for%20her%20part%2C%20is%20more%20than%20happy%20to%20extol%20the%20benefits%20of%20the%20sauna.%20She's%20still%20warming%20to%20the%20cold%20plunge%2C%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20if%20I%20can%20handle%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20tells%20me.%20%26quot%3BMaybe%20I'll%20go%20to%20another%20biohacking%20event%20and%20submit%20myself%20to%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fjames-rodriguez%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EJames%20Rodriguez%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20correspondent%20on%20Business%20Insider's%20Discourse%20team.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwellness-longevity-trends-reshaping-american-homes-real-estate-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782289381000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3a92c5d175c90a6a6fb04c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwellness-longevity-trends-reshaping-american-homes-real-estate-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Health-obsessed%20homebuyers%20are%20splurging%20on%20cold%20plunges%2C%20saunas%2C%20and%20cryotherapy%20chambers.%20Real%20estate's%20biggest%20flex%20isn't%20just%20for%20the%20uber-rich.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jrodriguez%40insider.com%20(James%20Rodriguez)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C