0room%20at%20the%20Hana%20Bank%20headquarters%20in%20Seoul.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3b379bace32b985cf8961d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224078%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESouth%20Korea's%20AI-fueled%20rally%20also%20leaves%20the%20market%20particularly%20vulnerable%20to%20any%20reversal%20in%20the%20global%20AI%20trade.%3Cp%3EJade%20Gao%2FAFP%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAsian%20stocks%20steadied%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20with%20South%20Korea's%20Kospi%20gaining%204.6%25%20in%20early%20trade%20before%20paring%20gains.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20moves%20followed%20a%20sharp%20rout%20in%20global%20technology%20stocks.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20sharp%20swings%20highlight%20Asia's%20growing%20exposure%20to%20shifts%20in%20AI%20and%20chip-stock%20sentiment.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAsian%20markets%20steadied%20on%20Wednesday%20after%20a%20bruising%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsouth-korea-kospi-plunges-ai-tech-hyperscaler-stock-market-selloff-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etech-led%20selloff%3C%2Fa%3E%20rattled%20global%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESouth%20Korea's%20benchmark%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Findex%2Fkospi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKospi%20index%3C%2Fa%3E%20rebounded%20as%20much%20as%204.6%25%20in%20early%20trade%20after%20plunging%2010%25%20on%20Tuesday.%20The%20index%20closed%203.3%25%20higher%20after%20trade%20turned%20volatile%20around%20midday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChip%20giants%20Samsung%20Electronics%20and%20SK%20Hynix%20closed%209.8%25%20and%201%25%20higher%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElsewhere%2C%20trading%20was%20mixed.%20Japan's%20Nikkei%20225%20ended%200.9%25%20lower.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHong%20Kong's%20Hang%20Seng%20Index%20gained%20as%20much%20as%201%25.%20Taiwan's%20Taiex%20lost%202.2%25%2C%20as%20heavyweight%20chipmaker%20TSMC%20closed%204%25%20lower.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20moves%20followed%20a%20sharp%20rout%20in%20global%20technology%20stocks%2C%20as%20investors%20dumped%20high-flying%20semiconductor%20and%20artificial-intelligence%20names.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPart%20of%20the%20move%20in%20tech%20reflects%20funds%20taking%20profits%20and%20recognising%20that%20the%20risk-reward%20profile%20has%20shifted%2C%20particularly%20given%20the%20crowded%20positioning%20across%20parts%20of%20the%20global%20AI%20infrastructure%20and%20memory%20complex%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Chris%20Weston%2C%20the%20head%20of%20research%20at%20Pepperstone%2C%20in%20a%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2F4FBcE%2F2%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22US%20stocks%20take%20a%20hit%20from%20chips%20sell-off%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22471%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20volatility%20highlights%20how%20exposed%20some%20of%20Asia's%20biggest%20equity%20markets%20have%20become%20to%20shifts%20in%20sentiment%20around%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-sachs-south-korea-kospi-stock-market-outlook-ai-boom-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ESouth%20Korea%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20among%20the%20world's%20best-performing%20stock%20markets%20this%20year%2C%20driven%20by%20a%20rally%20in%20semiconductor%20and%20AI-related%20shares.%20But%20that%20strong%20run%20has%20left%20the%20market%20vulnerable%20to%20any%20reversal%20in%20the%20global%20AI%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOverall%2C%20whether%20these%20moves%20continue%20will%20depend%20on%20whether%20the%20market%20believes%20the%20cashflows%20from%20deployment%20and%20diffusion%20of%20AI%20models%20justify%20the%20infrastructure%20build-out%20that%20we%20are%20seeing%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Michael%20Wan%