3D%5C%22A%20laptop%20with%20Claude%20Code%20AI%20stickers.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a19dd1cb4fb977f35981e49%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222509%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAnthropic's%20Claude%20Code%20has%20become%20one%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20AI%20coding%20tools.%3Cp%3EBloomberg%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAI%20startup%20Legion%20sued%20the%20government%20over%20losing%20access%20to%20Anthropic's%20top%20AI%20models.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELegion%20said%20the%20directive%20harmed%20its%20business.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20lawsuit%20adds%20another%20layer%20to%20Anthropic's%20clash%20with%20the%20Trump%20administration.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20AI%20startup%20just%20sued%20the%20US%20government%20for%20cutting%20its%20access%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-claude-fable-5-mythos-class-model-release-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAnthropic's%20top%20models%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20legal%20tech%20company%20Legion%20filed%20a%20suit%20in%20Washington%2C%20D.C.%20over%20a%20government%20order%20requiring%20Anthropic%20to%20keep%20its%20models%20Fable%205%20and%20Mythos%205%20away%20from%20foreign%20nationals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Anthropic%20said%20it%20would%20disable%20access%20to%20both%20models%20following%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-disable-mythos-fable-us-export-control-national-security-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eletter%20from%20the%20US%20government%3C%2Fa%3E%20asking%20it%20to%20bar%20foreign%20individuals%20and%20entities%20from%20using%20the%20products.%20The%20AI%20lab%20said%20this%20rule%20would%20bar%20some%20Anthropic%20employees%20from%20using%20the%20tools.%20In%20order%20to%20comply%2C%20the%20company%20initially%20disabled%20access%20for%20everyone.%20Last%20week%2C%20Anthropic%20restored%20access%20to%20Claude%20Fable%205%20with%20nationality-based%20access%20controls%20and%20enhanced%20onboarding%20compliance%20screening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Tuesday's%20complaint%2C%20Legion%20said%20that%20it%20was%20a%20US-based%20company%20that%20employs%20Canadian%20nationals%20who%20work%20remotely%20from%20Canada.%20It%20added%20that%20its%20litigation%20technology%20tools%20are%20built%20on%20top%20of%20frontier%20lab%20models%2C%20such%20as%20those%20from%20Anthropic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLegion%20is%20a%20commercial%20customer%20of%20Anthropic%20with%20a%20contractual%20right%20and%20license%20to%20access%20and%20use%20the%20Fable%205%20model%2C%20which%20was%20integral%20to%20building%20and%20operating%20its%20platform%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20wrote%20in%20the%20filing.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20directive%20took%20effect%2C%20Legion%20lost%20the%20latest%20tool%20at%20the%20center%20of%20its%20development%20instantaneously.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20added%20that%20the%20order%20caused%20it%20%26quot%3Bimmediate%2C%20irreparable%2C%20and%20existential%26quot%3B%20harm%20against%20competitors%20because%20the%20pace%20of%20AI%20development%20is%20so%20rapid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELegion%2C%20founded%20in%202024%20and%20based%20in%20San%20Jose%2C%20develops%20AI-powered%20litigation%20drafting%20software%20that%20helps%20lawyers%20automate%20pleadings%2C%20discovery%20requests%2C%20and%20other%20court%20documents.%20The%20company%20has%20fewer%20than%2010%20employees%20listed%20on%20LinkedIn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Commerce%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELegion's%20lawsuit%20adds%20another%20set%20of%20stakeholders%20to%20Anthropic's%20clash%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-federal-agencies-stop-using-anthropic-technology-department-defense-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETrump%20administration%20over%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20safety%20and%20government%20control%20over%20frontier%20AI%20models.%20It%20may%20be%20the%20first%20among%20suits%20from%20Anthropic%20customers%20who%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freaction-to-trump-controls-on-anthropic-fable-and-mythos-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecomplaining%20about%20losing%20access%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20its%20most%20powerful%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Anthropic%20first%20paused%20access%20to%20the%20model%2C%20it%20said%20that%20the%20government%20was%20concerned%20that%20someone%20might%20try%20a%20jailbreak%20of%20Fable%205.%20The%20company%20argued%20that%20cutting%20access%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bnarrow%20potential%20jailbreak%26quot%3B%20was%20overkill%20and%20would%20halt%20all%20new%20model%20deployments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flegion-ai-startup-suing-us-government-new-anthropic-model-fable5-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782278116000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3b63003d84808d83754d74%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flegion-ai-startup-suing-us-government-new-anthropic-model-fable5-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Legal%20tech%20company%20Legion%20filed%20a%20suit%20over%20a%20order%20requiring%20Anthropic%20to%20keep%20its%20models%20Fable%205%20and%20Mythos%205%20away%20from%20foreign%20nationals.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sgoel%40insider.com%20(Shubhangi%20Goel)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A98%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Leslie%20Jones%20Says%20It%20Was%20%E2%80%98Frustrating%E2%80%99%20That%20%E2%80%98SNL%E2%80%99%20Writers%20Always%20Typecast%20Her%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Girl%20That%20Was%20Angry%20and%20Beating%20Up%20People%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782277134000%2C%22vi