%221607%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESlash's%20employee%20AI%20coded%20a%20shooter%20game%20and%20accidentally%20billed%20the%20company%20%2480%2C000%20for%20it.%3Cp%3EScreenshot%20of%20shooter%20game%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFintech%20firm%20Slash%20got%20a%20rude%20shock%20when%20it%20saw%20one%20of%20its%20employees'%20AI%20bills.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20employee%20spent%20over%20%2480%2C000%20AI%20coding%20a%20brainrot%20shooter%20game.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESlash%20is%20encouraging%20people%20to%20play%20the%20game%20so%20it%20can%20write%20it%20off%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bmarketing%20expense.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFintech%20company%20Slash%20is%20touting%20a%20new%20product%20that%20doesn't%20quite%20fit%20in%20line%20with%20its%20usual%20offerings%20%E2%80%94%20an%20AI-coded%20shooter%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20X%20post%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20San%20Francisco-based%20company%20wrote%20that%20one%20of%20its%20employees%20racked%20up%20a%20hefty%20AI%20coding%20bill%20building%20a%20video%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20encouraged%20the%20company%20last%20week%20to%20start%20vibe%20coding%20more%20but%20%40nickbruhman%20burned%20%2480k%20in%20credits%20on%20the%20Slash%20card%20for%20a%20brainrot%20shooter%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPls%20play%20it%20so%20we%20can%20write%20this%20off%20as%20a%20marketing%20expense%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELiterally%20called%20%26quot%3BBrainrot%20shooter%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20is%20a%20bare-bones%20game%20set%20in%20a%20Minecraft-esque%20landscape%2C%20where%20the%20player%20has%20to%20shoot%20characters%20with%20internet-viral%20brainrot%20names%20like%20%26quot%3Bskibidi%20toilet%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Btung%20tung%20tung%20sahur.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrediction%20market%20Polymarket%20picked%20up%20the%20news%2C%20writing%20in%20an%20X%20post%3A%20%26quot%3BFintech%20startup%20Slash%20reveals%20it%20was%20forced%20to%20roll%20back%20its%20AI%20coding%20push%20after%20an%20employee%20burned%20%2480%2C000%20in%20tokens%20in%20the%20first%20week.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20employee%2C%20Slash's%20head%20of%20strategic%20verticals%2C%20Nicolas%20Brilliante%2C%20posted%20a%20screenshot%20that%20appeared%20to%20be%20a%20dashboard%20of%20his%20AI%20usage%2C%20showing%20he%20had%20spent%20%2481%2C267.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20was%20a%20genuine%20accident%2C%20i%20underestimated%20my%20own%20ability%2C%26quot%3B%20Brilliante%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20reposting%20a%20Polymarket%20X%20post%2C%20he%20wrote%3A%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20actually%20insane%2C%20am%20I%20going%20to%20become%20a%20case%20study%20for%20how%20AI%20spend%20can%20get%20out%20of%20control.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrilliante%20isn't%20the%20only%20employee%20who's%20been%20building%20things%20fast%20and%20furiously%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpylon-ceo-tokenmaxxing-era-coming-to-end-ai-spend-limits-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eera%20of%20tokenmaxxing%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Still%2C%20many%20companies%20are%20now%20looking%20at%20their%20AI%20spending%20with%20a%20more%20critical%20lens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20firms%20have%20found%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-bubble-heads-doomers-sam-altman-ai-costs-huge-issue-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20costs%3C%2Fa%3E%20did%20not%20translate%20into%20productivity%20gains%2C%20and%20have%20cut%20back%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-token-economy-spending-workplace-budgets-usage-caps-software-engineer-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20budgets%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20like%20Uber%2C%20Coinbase%2C%20and%20Walmart%20have%20now%20set%20caps%20on%20how%20much%20their%20employees%20can%20spend%20on%20AI%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-ai-c