Royal%20United%20Services%20Institute's%20Land%20Warfare%20Conference%20in%20London.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20corps%20planning%20cycle%20that%20once%20took%2072%20hours%20can%20now%20take%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20they're%20going%20to%20do%20with%20the%20other%2071%20hours%2C%20I%20do%20not%20know.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDubbed%20a%20%26quot%3Bdigital%20targeting%20web%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20UK%2C%20ASGARD%20is%20designed%20to%20gather%20and%20process%20battlefield%20data%20to%20help%20commanders%20find%20targets%2C%20make%20decisions%2C%20and%20coordinate%20attacks.%20It's%20one%20of%20several%20efforts%20by%20militaries%20to%20use%20AI%20to%20manage%20war%20zones%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpalantir-project-maven-ai-demonstration-pentagon-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPalantir's%20Maven%3C%2Fa%3E%20system%20for%20the%20Pentagon%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-delta-battlefield-tool-slashed-strike-times-on-russian-targets-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUkraine's%20Delta%20platform%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20UK%20announced%20last%20year%20that%20it%20plans%20to%20spend%201%20billion%20pounds%2C%20or%20about%20%241.3%20billion%2C%20on%20developing%20such%20systems%20for%20its%20own%20military.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWalker%20said%20ASGARD%20would%20allow%20a%20corps%20to%20attack%2010%20times%20as%20many%20targets%20in%20a%20single%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20fact%2C%20they're%20limited%20only%20by%20the%20munitions%20that%20are%20available%20to%20fire%20into%20the%20sky%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BASGARD%20is%20literally%20a%20digital%20juggernaut%20that%20is%20evolving%20every%208%20to%2012%20weeks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20British%20Army%2C%20a%20corps%20is%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20battlefield%20command%20structure%20and%20typically%20oversees%20logistics%2C%20intelligence%2C%20strategic%20strikes%2C%20and%20the%20deployment%20of%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20troops.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20ASGARD%20is%20a%20headquarters-level%20platform%2C%20used%20by%20top%20commanders%20who%20can%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-military-command-center-satellite-photos-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eaway%20from%20the%20actual%20battlefield%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Last%20month%2C%20the%20UK%20conducted%20an%20exercise%20that%20deployed%20the%20system%20from%20a%20tube%20station%20under%20Trafalgar%20Square%2C%20which%20Walker%20said%20on%20Tuesday%20was%20managing%20troops%20in%20Estonia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20makeshift%20headquarters%20in%20the%20train%20station%20was%20processing%2010%20terabytes%20of%20data%2C%20or%20%26quot%3Bnearly%20three%20months%20of%20non-stop%20high-definition%20Netflix%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20day%2C%20the%20British%20Army%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Government%20officials%20and%20media%20observe%20an%20exercise%20conducted%20in%20a%20tube%20station.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3b5430ace32b985cf8969b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20UK%20conducted%20a%20weekslong%20exercise%20in%20Charing%20Cross%20station%20that%20used%20the%20ASGARD%20system.%3Cp%3EWO2%20Jon%20Bevan%20Chief%2FUK%20Defense%20Ministry%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20ever%20think%20this%20was%20a%20moment%20where%20we%20had%20a%20conversation%20about%20what%20is%20our%20century's%20'tank%20versus%20horse'%20moment%2C%20I%20feel%20it's%20about%20this%20area%2C%26quot%3B%20Walker%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-lessons-british-army-unit-all-in-on-drones-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBritish%20Army%3C%2Fa%3E%20head%20also%20said%20the%20UK%20is%20sending%20thousands%20of%20drones%20to%20its%20units%20and%20introducing%2050%20operational-level%20electronic%20warfare%20systems%20that%20were%20used%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20prepare%20against%20Russia%2C%20a%20British%20corps%20needs%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bcapable%20of%20doing%20what%20a%20Ukrainian%20corps%20can%20do%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20in%20the%20next%20year%2C%20I%20expect%20to%20see%20much%20greater%20numbers%20of%20our%20remote%20and%20autonomous%20systems%20forward%20on%20our%20eastern%20flank%2C%20ready%20to%20strike%20and%20act%20within%2030%20minutes%2C%26quot%3B%20Walker%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbritish-army-head-war-planning-cycle-asgard-cut-72-hours-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782275447000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3b53133d84808d83754d3e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbritish-army-head-war-planning-cycle-asgard-cut-72-hours-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWhat%20they're%20going%20to%20do%20with%20the%20other%2071%20hours%2C%20I%20don't%20know%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gen.%20Roly%20Walker%2C%20adding%20that%20a%20corps%20could%20now%20hit%2010%20times%20as%20many%20targets.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mloh%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Loh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tan%20France%20says%20he%20writes%20emails%20so%20his%20kids%20can%20see%20who%20they%20were%20growing%20up%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224195%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tan%20France.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3b44296891755ad48b84e9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223146%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETan%20France%20says%20he's%20been%20documenting%20his%20kids'%20childhoods%20in%20emails.%3Cp%3EDave%20Benett%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETan%20France%20says%20he%20writes%20emails%20to%20his%20kids%20so%20they%20can%20revisit%20their%20childhoods%20one%20day.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20%26quot%3BQueer%20Eye%26quot%3B%20star%20said%20he%20also%20uses%20the%20messages%20to%20document%20what%20life%20was%20like%20for%20him%20and%20his%20husband%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BI%20find%20it%20fascinating%20to%20know%20that%20my%20kids%20might%20see%20us%20as%20just%20people%20also%2C%26quot%3B%20France%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftan-france-interview-baby-queer-eye-netflix-cover-story-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETan%20France%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20he%20writes%20messages%20to%20his%20kids%20that%20they%20won't%20read%20until%20they're%20older.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday's%20episode%20of%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DpyXTJ69Gy8c%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReclaiming%20with%20Monica%20Lewinsky%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20podcast%2C%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fqueer-eye-casting-director-shares-what-look-for-contestants-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EQueer%20Eye%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20star%20said%20he's%20been%20documenting%20his%20kids'%20childhoods%20through%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20created%20email%20accounts%20for%20my%20kids%2C%26quot%3B%20France%20told%20podcast%20host%20Monica%20Lewinsky.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20six%20months%20or%20so%2C%20France%20and%20his%20husband%2C%20Rob%20France%2C%20will%20each%20send%20their%20children%20emails%20%26quot%3Babout%20who%20they%20are%2C%20and%20what%20they're%20about%2C%20and%20what%20they%20enjoy%2C%20and%20who%20we%20think%20they%20might%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%2C%20who%20married%20in%202007%2C%20welcomed%20two%20children%20via%20surrogacy%20in%202021%20and%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrance%20said%20the%20email%20tradition%20is%20his%20%26quot%3Bfavorite%20thing%26quot%3B%20to%20do%20several%20times%20each%20year%2C%20and%20he%20loves%20the%20idea%20of%20his%20kids%20one%20day%20looking%20back%20on%20the%20messages%20as%20adults.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20that%2C%20he%20hopes%20the%20messages%20will%20offer%20his%20children%20a%20perspective%20he%20never%20had%20growing%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20love%20to%20know%20if%20my%20parents%20struggled%20as%20much%20as%20I'm%20struggling%20being%20a%20parent%2C%20and%20how%20hard%20it%20is%2C%20because%20we%20only%20just%20see%20our%20parents%20as%2C%20well%2C%20you're%20my%20parent%2C%26quot%3B%20France%20continued.%20%26quot%3BI%20find%20it%20fascinating%20to%20know%20that%20my%20kids%20might%20see%20us%20as%20just%20people%20also.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrance%20said%20he%20got%20the%20idea%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkim-kardashian-met-gala-looks-ranked%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKim%20Kardashian%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%202023%20appearance%20on%20the%20%26quot%3BOn%20Purpose%20with%20Jay%20Shetty%26quot%3B%20podcast%2C%20the%20Skims%20founder%20said%20she%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkim-kardashian-birthday-gift-writes-letters-kids-childhood-kanye-west-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewrites%20letters%20to%20her%20kids%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20their%20birthdays%20about%20the%20year%20they've%20had.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20that%20they'll%20appreciate%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Kardashian%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20celebrity%20parents%20have%20also%20spoken%20about%20preserving%20memories%20for%20their%20kids%20this%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeghan%20Markle%20said%20in%20a%202025%20appearance%20on%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DhSWpaFRvX6k%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Jamie%20Kern%20Lima%20S