%20was%20planning%20on%20not%20coming%20home.%20During%20the%20three-day%20break%2C%20I%20got%20a%20text%20that%20I%20was%20cut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20drove%20home%20with%20my%20basketball%20career%20behind%20me%20and%20no%20idea%20what%20was%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22775%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mother%20and%20son%20on%20a%20basketball%20court.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3900940e60dfb3f373ff25%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22581%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDougherty%20with%20his%20grandmother%20when%20he%20was%20still%20playing%20basketball.%3Cp%3EProvided%20by%20Jareb%20Dougherty%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22509f7fa6-b684-45a4-98a6-cc9284825851%5C%22%3EThe%20family%20business%20back%20home%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20was%20busy%20chasing%20my%20basketball%20dreams%2C%20my%20mother%2C%20Kristin%20Dougherty%2C%20landed%20a%20bartending%20job%20at%20Donovan's%20Irish%20Pub%20in%20St.%20Augustine%20after%20responding%20to%20a%20Craigslist%20ad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20when%20I%20was%20still%20in%20college%2C%20my%20mom%20arrived%20at%20work%20and%20found%20an%20eviction%20notice%20on%20the%20door.%20She%20later%20heard%20that%20the%20owners%20were%20behind%20on%20rent%20and%20taxes.%20As%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingle-mom-struggle-affordability-new-york-city-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esingle%20mom%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20my%20dad%20died%20when%20I%20was%20a%20toddler%20%E2%80%94%20she'd%20always%20worked%20in%20the%20food%20industry%20to%20support%20us.%20She%20took%20this%20as%20her%20moment%20to%20level%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20figured%20out%20a%20way%20to%20buy%20the%20restaurant.%20She%20was%20following%20my%20grandfather's%20footsteps%2C%20who%20was%20always%20putting%20a%20bug%20in%20her%20ear%20to%20buy%20the%20business%20wherever%20she%20worked.%20Her%20brother%20helped%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-start-a-business-according-to-successful-entrepreneurs-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etake%20over%20the%20business%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20my%20basketball%20career%20suddenly%20ended%2C%20I%20came%20back%20to%20the%20restaurant%20to%20bartend%20and%20save%20money%20until%20I%20figured%20out%20my%20life.%20More%20curveballs%20were%20on%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227c559885-b77e-43cd-ba7c-f5c15f03e9f6%5C%22%3EStepping%20up%20to%20my%20future%20career%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20having%20never%20pictured%20a%20career%20in%20the%20restaurant%20business%2C%20when%20my%20mother%20and%20her%20brother%20had%20a%20falling%20out%2C%20I%20knew%20she%20needed%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20at%2026%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20buy%20my%20uncle's%20shares%20in%20the%20restaurant.%20I%20had%20saved%20up%20a%20good%20amount%20from%20part-time%20jobs%20and%20took%20a%20loan%20from%20another%20family%20member.%20I%20had%20never%20run%20a%20business%2C%20but%20I%20knew%20my%20mom%20needed%20help%2C%20and%20I%20jumped%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20being%20mostly%20equal%20partners%2C%20I've%20told%20her%20that%20she%20always%20has%20the%20final%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22272edf1b-fcc8-4fce-a4ca-066123c088d6%5C%22%3ECo-owning%20a%20pub%20with%20my%20mother%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20might%20say%20don't%20mix%20business%20and%20family%2C%20I%20can't%20see%20it%20any%20other%20way.%20My%20mom%20is%20my%20best%20friend%2C%20and%20we%20even%20lived%20together%20until%20recently.%20I'm%2029%20and%20decided%20to%20invest%20in%20a%20place%20for%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELiving%20and%20working%20together%20was%20easy%20for%20us.%20Learning%20to%20run%20a%20business%20was%20not.%20For%20six%20months%2C%20neither%20of%20us%20took%20a%20paycheck.%20We%20had%20to%20replace%20equipment%20while%20money%20was%20tight.%20When%20we%20finally%20got%20our%20first%20check%2C%20we%20could%20breathe%20for%20a%20moment%20%E2%80%94%20I%20realized%20this%20could%20actually%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22791%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20son%2C%20mom%2C%20and%20grandma%20sitting%20at%20a%20table%20together.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3a01a6d175c90a6a6face9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22481%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDougherty%20now%20runs%20the%20restaurant%20with%20his%20mom%3B%20his%20grandma%20prepares%20homemade%20desserts.%3Cp%3EProvided%20by%20Jareb%20Dougherty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20to%20get%20used%20to%20managing%20people%2C%20including%20their%20emotions%2C%20time%2C%20and%20schedules.%20With%2028%20employees%2C%20there%20are%20lots%20of%20personalities%20to%20handle.%20During%20busy%20hours%2C%20cooks%20can%20get%20grumpy%20and%20servers%20yell%20for%20orders.%20But%20that's%20restaurant%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20essential%20change%20from%20when%20my%20mom%20and%20her%20brother%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fartificial-intelligence-digital-coworkers-restaurants-staff-starbucks-burger-king-chipotle-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eran%20the%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20who%20was%20responsible%20for%20which%20parts%20of%20the%20restaurant.%20With%20them%2C%20he%20ran%20the%20back%20of%20the%20house%2C%20and%20she%20ran%20the%20front%20of%20the%20house.%20This%20didn't%20work%20because%20they%20both%20had%20to%20be%20there%20all%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20my%20mom%20and%20I%20both%20run%20everything%2C%20so%20we%20can%20give%20each%20other%20breaks.%20She's%20a%20workaholic%20with%20a%20crazy%20work%20ethic%2C%20so%20I%20have%20to%20make%20sure%20she%20takes%20days%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22776cabf0-dee0-4ca8-8929-06b5be7840d0%5C%22%3EBuilding%20toward%20a%20bigger%20future%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELife%20is%20enjoyable%20these%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20basketball%20career%20is%20behind%20me%2C%20except%20for%20occasionally%20shooting%20hoops%20with%20friends.%20Sometimes%20that%20devastating%20text%20%E2%80%94%20and%20what%20could%20have%20been%20%E2%80%94%20still%20plays%20in%20my%20mind.%20I%20think%20that's%20true%20for%20most%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpro-athletes-share-personal-finance-investing-retirement-advice-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eretired%20athletes%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20what's%20in%20front%20of%20me%20is%20exciting%2C%20and%20I'm%20always%20on%20call%2C%20ready%20for%20the%20next%20phone%20call%20from%20someone%20who%20needs%20me%20at%20the%20restaurant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20grandma%20is%20a%20prep%20cook%20there%20and%20makes%20homemade%20desserts.%20I%20actually%20enjoy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-business-advice-of-2025-from-successful-entrepreneurs-side-hustlers-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erunning%20a%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20my%20family.%20We%20discuss%20every%20decision%20together%20and%20consider%20the%20restaurant%20our%20home%20away%20from%20home.%20We%20recently%20launched%20a%20traditional%20Irish%20brunch%20featuring%20rashers%2C%20a%20type%20of%20Irish%20bacon%2C%20and%20blood%20sausage%2C%20although%20fish%20and%20chips%20remains%20our%20most%20popular%20dish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20live%20a%20life%20I%20never%20envisioned%20for%20myself%2C%20but%20it's%20also%20one%20I%20wouldn't%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprofessional-basketball-career-irish-pub-working-with-mom-family-restaurant-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782274426000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a38ff2ec7a58f814f0d4e1e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprofessional-basketball-career-irish-pub-working-with-mom-family-restaurant-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20Jareb%20Dougherty%