A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jeffrey%20Epstein%20pitched%20his%20connections%20with%20billionaires%20to%20get%20close%20to%20Bill%20Gates%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221983%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Terje%20Rod%20Larsen%20Bill%20Gates%20Jeffrey%20Epstein%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3b29da6891755ad48b8459%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221487%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBill%20Gates%20had%20several%20dinners%20in%20Jeffrey%20Epstein's%20Manhattan%20mansion.%20He%20told%20Congress%20the%20conversations%20revolved%20around%20philanthropy.%3Cp%3EUS%20Department%20of%20Justice%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBill%20Gates%20told%20Congress%20Jeffrey%20Epstein%20pitched%20him%20on%20his%20connections%20to%20billionaires.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGates%20said%20he%20believed%20Epstein%20could%20direct%20the%20money%20of%20billionaires'%20estates%20to%20his%20foundation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGates%20also%20said%20Epstein%20wormed%20his%20way%20into%20his%20life%20with%20%26quot%3Bveiled%20threats%26quot%3B%20to%20disclose%20affairs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhy%20did%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fepstein-worked-aggressively-to-score-2013-meeting-with-bill-gates-2019-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBill%20Gates%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20so%20many%20meetings%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbill-gates-testimony-jeffrey-epstein-meetings-grave-error-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJeffrey%20Epstein%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Microsoft%20founder%2C%20Epstein%20had%20something%20few%20other%20people%20could%20offer%3A%20connections%20to%20billionaires%20planning%20where%20their%20money%20would%20go%20when%20they%20died.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ultrawealthy%20sex%20offender%20had%20pitched%20himself%20as%20someone%20who%20could%20help%20bring%20enormous%20sums%20of%20money%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbill-and-melinda-gates-foundation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGates%20Foundation%3C%2Fa%3E's%20global%20health%20initiatives%20from%20Wall%20Street%20and%20Middle%20East%20billionaires%20figuring%20out%20their%20estate%20plans%2C%20Gates%20told%20a%20congressional%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20because%20of%20his%20purported%20relationship%20with%20billionaires%2C%20and%20because%20he%20was%20part%20of%20those%20tax%20and%20will%20discussions%2C%20that%20it%20seemed%20credible%20to%20me%20that%20he%20might%20be%20able%20to%20raise%20%E2%80%94%20or%20be%20a%20referral%20source%20to%20help%20raise%20%E2%80%94%20billions%20of%20dollars%20for%20global%20health%2C%26quot%3B%20Gates%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGates%20described%20his%20relationship%20with%20Epstein%20in%20a%20June%2010%20interview%20with%20the%20House%20Oversight%20Committee%20that%20lasted%20nearly%20six%20hours.%20The%20committee%2C%20which%20is%20investigating%20Epstein's%20relationships%20with%20powerful%20people%2C%20released%20a%20transcript%20on%20Tuesday%20afternoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGates%20said%20he%20had%20at%20least%20a%20dozen%20meetings%20with%20Epstein%20%E2%80%94%20at%20his%20Manhattan%20mansion%2C%20on%20a%20private%20jet%2C%20and%20over%20Skype%20%E2%80%94%20between%202011%20and%202014.%20He%20said%20the%20discussions%20in%20those%20meetings%20revolved%20around%20raising%20funds%20for%20philanthropy%2C%20and%20that%20he%20regrets%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGates%20hasn't%20been%20accused%20of%20any%20sexual%20misconduct%20related%20to%20Epstein%20%E2%80%94%20who%20pleaded%20guilty%20in%202008%20to%20sex%20offenses%20in%20Florida%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeffrey-epstein-death-autopsy-doctor-explains-delayed-suicide-ruling-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edied%20in%20jail%20in%202019%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20awaiting%20trial%20on%20more%20severe%20federal%20sex-trafficking%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20interview%20with%20members%20of%20the%20House%20Oversight%20Committee%2C%20Gates%20disclosed%20that%20he%20had%20previously%20cooperated%20with%20a%20law%20enforcement%20investigation%20into%20Epstein%2C%20sitting%20for%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjp-morgan-jpmorgan-virgin-islands-blame-not-stopping-jeffrey-epstein-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUS%20Virgin%20Islands%3C%2Fa%3E%20investigators%20into%20Epstein's%20sex-trafficking%20operation.%20Gates%20apologized%20for%20allowing%20Epstein%20to%20use%20him%20to%20improve%20his%20own%20reputation%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20his%20initial%20criminal%20conviction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20see%20now%20that%20he%20sought%20to%20build%20an%20image%20of%20legitimacy%20around%20himself%20using%20connections%20to%20reputable%20and%20powerful%20people%20to%20deflect%20scrutiny%20and%20attempt%20to%20rehabilitate%20his%20reputation%2C%26quot%3B%20Gates%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEpstein%20often%20told%20people%20that%20he%20made%20his%20money%20by%20managing%20the%20money%20of%20billionaires.%20His%20estate%2C%20which%20included%20his%20Manhattan%20mansion%2C%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeffrey-epstein-files-reveal-islands-renovation-designs-photos-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eisland%20in%20the%20US%20Virgin%20Islands%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20was%20valued%20at%20%24630%20million%20after%20his%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20only%20known%20billionaire%20financial%20clients%20were%20former%20L%20Brands%20CEO%20Les%20Wexner%20and%20former%20Apollo%20Global%20Management%20CEO%20Leon%20Black%2C%20both%20of%20whom%20cut%20ties%20with%20Epstein%20after%20accusing%20him%20of%20acting%20dishonestly%20with%20their%20money.%20The%20Epstein%20files%20released%20by%20the%20Justice%20Department%20showed%20that%20he%20unsuccessfully%20tried%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeffrey-epstein-files-playbook-landing-billionaire-clients-mort-zuckerman-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econvince%20Mort%20Zuckerman%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20billionaire%20real%20estate%20and%20media%20mogul%2C%20to%20hand%20over%20control%20of%20his%20finances%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Gates%2C%20Epstein%20said%20he%20could%20direct%20his%20clients'%20money%20to%20the%20Gates%20Foundation%20as%20part%20of%20their%20%26quot%3Btax%20and%20will%20discussions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20key%20time%20when%20people%20think%20that%20through%20is%20when%20they're%20doing%20their%20will%20%E2%80%94%20how%20much%20goes%20to%20their%20children%2C%26quot%3B%20Gates%20told%20the%20House%20Oversight%20Committee.%20%26quot%3BFor%20people%20who%20are%20very%20rich%2C%20hopefully%20they%20think%20of%20a%20large%20sum%20being%20available%20for%20philanthropy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEpstein%20used%20his%20relationship%20with%20Gates%20to%20maintain%20ties%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjpmorgan-chase-drawn-out-breakup-with-jeffrey-epstein-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJPMorgan%20Chase%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeffrey-epstein-accountant-harry-beller-cash-withdrawals-jpmorgan-congress-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eraised%20red%20flags%20when%20his%20accounts%3C%2Fa%3E%20withdrew%20large%20sums%20of%20cash%20in%20the%20years%20following%20his%202008%20conviction.%20Epstein%20pitched%20two%20of%20the%20bank's%20executives%2C%20Jes%20Staley%20and%20Mary%20Erdoes%2C%20on%20the%20idea%20of%20setting%20up%20a%20donor-advised%20fund%20for%20the%20Gates%20Foundation's%20Global%20Health%20Program%20at%20the%20bank%2C%20according%20to%20emails%20obtained%20through%20a%20now-settled%20lawsuit%20by%20US%20Virgin%20Islands%20against%20JPMorgan%20Chase.%20Gates%20told%20the%20House%20Oversight%20Committee%20that%20he%20discussed%20the%20donor-advised%20fund%20with%20Epstein%20%26quot%3Bbut%20it%20was%20a%20dead%20end.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Epstein%20files%20released%20by%20the%20Justice%20Department%20show%20that%20Epstein%20communicated%20with%20former%20Microsoft%20executives%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fsteven-sinofsky%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESteven%20Sinofsky%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnathan-myhrvold-on-bill-gates-genius-for-finding-best-ideas%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENathan%20Myhrvold%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20former%20board%20member%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freid-hoffman-discloses-more-meetings-jeffrey-epstein-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EReid%20Hoffman%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Gates%20told%20the%20committee%20he%20was%20unaware%20of%20their%20relationships%20with%20Epstein.%20Gates%20said%20he%20wasn't%20knowledgeable%20about%20Epstein's%20relationship%20with%20Melanie%20Walker%2C%20a%20former%20Gates%20Foundation%20employee%20with%20whom%20Epstein%20frequently%20communicated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221428%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22jes%20staley%20larry%20summers%20jeffrey%20epstein%20bill%20gates%20boris%20nikolic%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3b2bae3d84808d83754c76%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221071%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFormer%20JPMorgan%20executive%20Jes%20Staley%2C%20former%20Treasury%20Secretary%20Larry%20Summers%2C%20Jeffrey%20Epstein%2C%20Bill%20Gates%2C%20and%20Boris%20Nikolic%20were%20photographed%20together%20after%20a%20dinner%20in%20Epstein's%20home.%3Cp%3EUS%20Department%20of%20Justice%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAside%20from%20fruitless%20discussions%20about%20philanthropy%2C%20Epstein%20wormed%20his%20way%20into%20Gates'%20life%20in%20more%20sinister%20ways%2C%20Gates%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGates%20told%20Congress%20he%20first%20met%20Epstein%20in%202011%2C%20following%20an%20introduction%20by%20Boris%20Nikolic%2C%20who%20at%20the%20time%20was%20a%20science%20advisor%20to%20his%20foundation.%20Representatives%20for%20Nikolic%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENikolic%20knew%20about%20extramarital%20affairs%20Gates%20had%20with%20two%20women%2C%20Gates%20said.%20Emails%20released%20by%20the%20Justice%20Department%20show%20that%20Nikolic%20sought%20Epstein's%20advice%20on%20extracting%20a%20favorable%20exit%20package%20when%20he%20stopped%20working%20for%20the%20foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEpstein%20knew%20about%20those%20two%20affairs%20and%20appeared%20to%20be%20friendly%20with%20a%20third%20woman%20he%20had%20an%20affair%20with%2C%20Gates%20told%20Congress.%20Epstein%20made%20%26quot%3Bveiled%20threats%26quot%3B%20to%20disclose%20those%20affairs%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20never%20blackmailed%20me%2C%20but%20looking%20at%20these%20emails%2C%20it%20raises%20a%20serious%20probability%20that%20he%20contemplated%20blackmailing%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Gates%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20one%20occasion%20%E2%80%94%20after%20Gates%20said%20he%20cut%20ties%20with%20Epstein%2C%20in%20December%202014%20%E2%80%94%20Epstein%20asked%20Gates%20to%20reimburse%20him%20for%20several%20thousand%20dollars%20in%20expenses%20related%20to%20one%20of%20the%20women%20Gates%20had%20an%20affair%20with%2C%20emails%20show.%20Gates%20didn't%20pay%20it%20and%20said%20he%20viewed%20the%20request%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20tactic%26quot%3B%20to%20re-engage%20with%20the%20sex%20offender.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20took%20that%20on%20very%20explicitly%20and%20said%2C%20'Look%2C%20if%20you%20think%20you're%20going%20to%20get%20more%20money%20out%20of%20this%2C%20it's%20not%20going%20to%20happen%2C%20and%20if%20that%20means%20you%20go%20out%20and%20talk%20to%20people%20about%20things%2C%20I%20will%20just%20bear%20the%20pain%20of%20that%20and%20deal%20with%20it%2C'%26quot%3B%20Gates%20told%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbill-gates-jeffrey-epstein-congress-billionaire-connections-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782263714000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3b30faace32b985cf895fd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbill-gates-jeffrey-epstein-congress-billionaire-connections-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bill%20Gates%20told%20Congress%20that%20Jeffrey%20Epstein%20wormed%20his%20way%20into%20his%20life%20with%20%26quot%3Bveiled%20threats%26quot%3B%20to%20disclose%20extramarital%20affairs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jshamsian%40businessinsider.com%20(Jacob%20Shamsian)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A95%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Best%20Prime%20Day%20Oura%20Ring%20deals%3A%20Save%20up%20to%2051%25%20on%20one%20of%20our%20favorite%20smart%20rings%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20buy%20through%20our%20links%2C%20Business%20Insider%20may%20earn%20an%20affiliate%20commission.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-reviews-expertise-in-product-reviews%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELearn%20more%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20Oura%20Ring%204s%20are%20displayed%20on%20a%20blue%20gradient%20background%20with%20a%20blue%20%26quot%3BPrime%20Day%20Deals%202026%26quot%3B%20badge%20in%20the%20foreground.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3af9603d84808d83754ba9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Oura%20Ring%204%20is%20majorly%20discounted%20for%20this%20year's%20Prime%20Day%20event.%3Cp%3EAmazon%3B%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20Prime%20Day%20is%20officially%20here%2C%20and%20some%20of%20the%20top%