y.%3Cp%3EMeta%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMark%20Zuckerberg%20envisions%20Meta's%20AI%20glasses%20as%20stylish%2C%20functional%20wearables%2C%20not%20mere%20gadgets.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMeta's%20new%20AI%20glasses%2C%20starting%20at%20%24299%2C%20aim%20to%20blend%20fashion%20with%20advanced%20wearable%20technology.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EZuckerberg%20said%20his%20collaboration%20with%20EssilorLuxottica%20influenced%20his%20taste%20in%20fashion.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMark%20Zuckerberg%20wants%20Meta's%20latest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-ray-ban-smart-glasses-facial-recognition-distracted-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20glasses%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20be%20more%20than%20a%20gadget.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-ai-training-data-leak-exposed-employee-activity-across-company-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMeta%20CEO%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20challenge%20isn't%20cramming%20more%20AI%20into%20a%20pair%20of%20frames%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20making%20glasses%20people%20actually%20want%20to%20wear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20an%20interview%20with%20Feed%20Me%20creator%20Emily%20Sundberg%2C%20Zuckerberg%20sounded%20less%20like%20a%20Silicon%20Valley%20executive%20and%20more%20like%20a%20fashion%20designer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20there's%20going%20to%20be%20a%20spectrum%20both%20of%20styles%20and%20different%20amounts%20of%20functionality%20and%20different%20price%20points%2C%26quot%3B%20Zuckerberg%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20the%20challenge%20is%20that%20each%20one%20you%20need%20to%20hit%20the%20sweet%20spot%20of%20making%20it%20good-looking%20and%20comfortable%20to%20wear%20and%20delivering%20on%20the%20functionality.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20pretty%20involved%20in%20everything%20we%20build%2C%26quot%3B%20Zuckerberg%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20Meta%20unveiled%20a%20new%20line%20of%20smart%20glasses%20starting%20at%20%24299%2C%20cheaper%20than%20the%20company's%20entry-level%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-ray-ban-prank-videos-problem-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERay-Ban%20glasses%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20it%20pushes%20harder%20into%20wearable%20technology.%20The%20new%20glasses%20were%20developed%20with%20eyewear%20giant%20EssilorLuxottica%20but%20don't%20carry%20Ray-Ban%20or%20Oakley%20branding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZuckerberg%20said%20working%20on%20smart%20glasses%20has%20exposed%20him%20to%20a%20different%20set%20of%20priorities%20than%20the%20software%20world.%20Through%20Meta's%20partnership%20with%20EssilorLuxottica%2C%20he%20said%20he%20learned%20about%20%26quot%3Bhow%20they%20build%20their%20brands%2C%20how%20they%20do%20their%20design%2C%20what%20they%20feel%20is%20important.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Meta%20CEO%20developed%20some%20fashion%20interests%20of%20his%20own%20and%20evolved%20from%20what%20he%20said%20used%20to%20be%20his%20favorite%20item%20back%20in%20the%20aughts%3A%20Adidas%20slides.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221650%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Founder%20of%20Facebook.com%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%2C%20right%2C%20and%20Dustin%20Moscovitz%2C%20co-founder%2C%20left%3B%20have%20their%20photo%20taken%20at%20Harvard%20Yard.%20The%20two%20are%20students%20at%20Harvard%20University%20who%20are%20taking%20the%20semester%20off.%20(Photo%20by%20Justine%20Hunt%2FThe%20Boston%20Globe%20via%20Getty%20Images)%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3b03956891755ad48b83a4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221175%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EZuckerberg%2C%20right%2C%20and%20Dustin%20Moscovitz%2C%20left.%20Zuckerberg%20was%20wearing%20his%20Adidas%20slides.%3Cp%3EJustine%20Hunt%2FThe%20Boston%20Globe%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20future%20is%20going%20to%20be%20these%20different%20wearable%20platforms%20that%20I%20think%20merge%20with%20fashion%2C%26quot%3B%20Zuckerberg%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Zuckerberg%2C%20the%20future%20of%20AI%20hardware%20may%20need%20to%20look%20more%20like%20runway%20fashion%20than%20gaming%20accessories%2C%20and%20that%20mindset%20is%20increasingly%20shaping%20Meta's%20wearable%20ambitions%20as%20rivals%2C%20including%20Google%20and%20Snap%2C%20race%20into%20AI-powered%20eyewear.%20Snap's%20new%20AI%20glasses%2C%20for%20example%2C%20immediately%20received%20online%20rebuff%20for%20being%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsnap-specs-ar-glasses-debut-price-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eexpensive%20and%20clunky%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20launching%20earlier%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20think%20the%20key%20for%20any%20one%20of%20these%2C%26quot%3B%20Zuckerberg%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BWhether%20it's%20on%20your%20wrist%20or%20on%20your%20face%20or%20anything%20else%2C%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20something%20that%20you're%20proud%20to%20wear%20and%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20comfortable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-meta-glasses-style-comfort-tech-wearable-fashion-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782253972000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3af40eace32b985cf894d1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-meta-glasses-style-comfort-tech-wearable-fashion-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mark%20Zuckerberg's%20latest%20obsession%20is%20fashion%2C%20which%20he%20sees%20as%20key%20to%20getting%20more%20people%20to%20wear%20Meta's%20AI%20glasses%20as%20more%20than%20tech%20gadgets.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22katherineli%40insider.com%20(Katherine%20Li)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A94%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Best%20Dyson%20hair%20tool%20Prime