Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20tough%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20admits.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20I%20never%20let%20my%20struggles%20show%20in%20front%20of%20my%20students.%20They%20deserve%20my%20full%20attention.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMore%20than%20a%20teacher%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESangeeta%E2%80%99s%20role%20extends%20beyond%20academics.%20She%20eats%20midday%20meals%20sitting%20cross-legged%20with%20the%20children.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20they%20see%20me%20eating%20from%20the%20same%20kind%20of%20plate%20as%20theirs%2C%20they%20feel%20I%20am%20one%20of%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20seasonal%20fevers%2C%20she%20keeps%20basic%20medicines%20in%20the%20staffroom.%20%E2%80%9COn%20days%20when%20rice%20is%20served%20in%20the%20midday%20meal%2C%20I%20avoid%20giving%20it%20to%20sick%20children%2C%20as%20rice%20is%20believed%20to%20aggravate%20colds.%20Instead%2C%20I%20share%20my%20tiffin%20with%20them%20before%20giving%20medicine%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20school%20day%20officially%20ends%20at%202%20PM%2C%20but%20the%20work%20continues%20%E2%80%94%20preparing%20lesson%20plans%2C%20completing%20paperwork%2C%20and%20visiting%20families%20whose%20children%20miss%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20true%20reward%20of%20teaching%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Sangeeta%2C%20teaching%20has%20never%20been%20just%20a%20job.%20It%20is%20a%20mission.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20villages%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F261821%2Finspiring-uttarakhand-teacher-pandemic-village-students-lockdown%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eteaching%20is%20as%20much%20about%20care%20%3C%2Fa%3Eas%20it%20is%20about%20books.%20You%20have%20to%20build%20trust%2C%20spark%20curiosity%2C%20and%20show%20children%20that%20education%20can%20change%20their%20lives.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20pauses%2C%20then%20adds%2